Description: Reinstate desktop overrides
 Upstream no longer wants to use desktop overrides.
 Reinstate these for Debian & Ubuntu to ensure
 clean separation from Budgie and GNOME desktops
Author: David Mohammed <fossfreedom@ubuntu.com>
Forwarded: not-needed
Last-Update: 2019-03-09


